			<a name="Double_Slit_Experiment" id="Double_Slit_Experiment"></a><h1> <span class="mw-headline"> Double Slit Experiment </span></h1>
<p>A first attempt at a double slit experiment, showing 2D interference fringes from two point sources situated 2 cm from each other recorded on a 20x20 cm 2D PSD.
The detector is situated 1 m downstream from the source assembly. 
</p>
<table class="gallery" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td><div class="gallerybox" style="width: 155px;">
